Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.67,1:27:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,God wrote that song.\NIt represent an aspect of God
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.12,1:27:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that cannot be verbalized\Nbeyond intellectual.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.80,1:27:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,coming off the coast, the Pacific coast\Nin California one time. I looked up
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.00,1:27:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,above and here were these giant these\Nhuge birds
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.56,1:27:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and the wind was coming off the ocean\Nand the way the birds maintained themsel
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.80,1:27:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,there. They did not flap their wings.\NThese giant birds were just angled
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.76,1:28:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,himself against the wind like so and\Nlike so and like so like so. The bird
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.15,1:28:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,just made the most minute movements\Nand instead it took advantage of the
