Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.36,1:28:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,energy, the birds stayed up there for\Nlike half an hour, an hour at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.60,1:28:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All they did was move their little\Nbodies a slight half an inch this way
