Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.19,1:29:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It uplifts you and sustains you\N>> through a whole lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.96,1:29:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The winds of God sustain us.\NWe thank thee oh Lord
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.00,1:29:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,for this life\Nfor the beauty
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.63,1:29:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of this life.\NWe're the real power of beauty
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.92,1:30:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is nonverbal.\NThe minute you hear this particular
