Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.00,1:30:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What it expresses is grace.\NThe grace of God
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.60,1:30:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,>> part of God's grace\N>> is the awareness of beauty.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.32,1:30:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who do not walk in God's grace\Nare oblivious to beauty,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.67,1:30:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,oblivious to kindness.\NSo it's love at the highest level.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.96,1:30:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a name. Love\Nagape. Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.56,1:31:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Transcends personal love. I guess\Nsee you cannot reach God
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.08,1:31:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,by bypassing love.\NThe bird cannot get all the way up to a
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.84,1:31:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,higher elevation without going through\Nthese various layers.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.28,1:31:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So we position ourself in a loving way.\NWe say thank you God
