Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.28,1:32:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's ask.\NTakes many lifetimes to earn
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.63,1:32:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to be here. Is this Wow.\NSo
